Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:12.42,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,What are these lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:16.02,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I'm sure that I've never known a view such as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.61,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Do you find the lights strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.53,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What about the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:38.74,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What about the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:42.96,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Just these lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.50,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Why would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:56.80,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,To her, someone who has been here her entire life, these lights are natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.70,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,“These must be shadows!” is what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:04.81,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,But a shadow always comes with an object that causes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:07.81,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,If so, then where would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:10.36,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:15.61,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,for you to find this strange, there must be\Nsome other scene that you {\i1}do{\i0\fscx40} {\r} find familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:21.22,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I dig through my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:28.13,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I was in a different world a long time ago…\Nor perhaps the distant future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:31.15,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I still retain the memory that I was once there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:19.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:22.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:27.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I caught a glance of you, so I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's fine, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:33.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We still can't get new members, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.70,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.38,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.74,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.50,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Looks like he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.13,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're just going to leave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.40,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm joking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, did you get hurt at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:06.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.09,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Awfully close now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.28,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Calling her by her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Are you two dating now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.19,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Have you kissed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:21.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I-I'm only having Okazaki-san help me reestablish the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're not dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.57,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.81,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:35.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, are you really not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When did I start calling you by your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:41.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:49.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I almost remembered something just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:55.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Something very warm…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…nostalgic…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's get going, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:09.92,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 10
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:09.92,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}The Genius Girl's Challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.04,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Recruiting members for the drama club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, there won't be anything fun even if you tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:19.57,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't be such a stranger. I want to help Nagisa-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:23.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you seriously like Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I've never loved anyone so seriously before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:33.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In the library up ahead, there's a mysterious and\Nbeautiful girl who is always reading difficult books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:36.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you talk to her, she occasionally gives you food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:40.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really cute, innocent, smart,\Nand it looks like she doesn't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.27,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Please introduce me to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think she's there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:44.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Go check her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.78,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.79,Note,,0,0,0,,Library
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is he doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.57,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I was com—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,—pletely ignored!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That was a long pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:07.43,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She won't react to small or sweet talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:12.60,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It pissed me off, so I threw books everywhere and knocked bookshelves over, but she still ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.64,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Who the hell is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:17.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's Ichinose Kotomi. You know the name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Ichinose Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.27,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That famous genius girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:25.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So basically she lives in a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That was a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A person in a different world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.14,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.43,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:58.94,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun. You can't make a mess like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:01.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You never change, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.18,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,The drama club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I told you about it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're recruiting members.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want to go see the club president after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.86,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,She won't bully me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's one thing that'll never happen, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:17.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's the new member candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on, introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.96,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello, Tomoya-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:29.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Say your name first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.34,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:33.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You spell Kotomi with three hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.89,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,When you speak to me, call me Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm Nagisa, spelled with one kanji character.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,People refer to me differently though…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.36,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can't you guys talk about anything other than your names?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.65,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My last name is Ichinose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mine's Furukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.61,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm in Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.66,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Type A blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm type A, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.28,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Pork cutlet sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Anpan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.45,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's no longer making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:08.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Despite her appearance, she's really smart,\Nso she doesn't need to study for entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:12.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She likes books, so she has a good vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So, as a candidate for new member, she's a perfect…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.94,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Is this Tamatebako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.94,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Tamatebako: A box from the story Urashima Tarou with smoke inside that ages those who get covered by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, you say something to her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm jealous of how beautiful your hair is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No! I'm telling you to talk her into joining the drama club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You practiced the speech, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Say things like, “Let's shed the tears of youth together”, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.88,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Do I have to cry?{ep 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:48.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,When the scene requires it,\Nthen there are times you have to. {ep 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.98,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I don't want to cry. {ep 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Still when you have to, you have to. {ep 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.47,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan, are you a bully? {ep 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No. I'm not a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.11,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's the Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you like the Big Dango Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:15.86,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.33,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll walk Kotomi back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.01,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Today, I was a little scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:35.80,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm always like that when I talk to a person I've just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.51,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But Nagisa-chan was kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:43.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you're so scared of others,\Nwhy were you able to talk with me so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan is a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.69,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Her Big Dango Family pictures were good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll just leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.25,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Is Nagisa-chan your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:00.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why did both you and Kyou ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:01.88,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The class representative of Class E and a vicious little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:08.71,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, Tomoya-kun.\NThere's a place I want to stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You really take everything at your own pace, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You really like books, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:20.57,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I can't become a well-established person if I don't study a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:43.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop it, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:50.03,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:57.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No matter how much you like books,\Nyou can't cut those in the library or bookstores.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:00.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you must, copy what you need onto a piece of paper…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Actually, you might get yelled at for that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.13,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:11.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You really should socialize with others more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.65,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Will she bully me? Will she bully me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She won't, so introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.24,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello, Tomoya-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay, that was good practice. Now for the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:28.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So? What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.25,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.17,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.17,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You spell Kotomi with three hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.26,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,When you speak to me, call me Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.01,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.65,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Is she a bully?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.25,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,She's the famous genius girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:46.46,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why is she hanging out with a bum like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a bum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.68,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Will she bully me? Will she bully me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.68,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've got lots of friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:12:00.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you can be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.98,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Isn't there something strange about becoming friends because you're asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:07.79,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Friends aren't given; you're supposed to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of all the times for her to spit out common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:14.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Besides, why are you taking care of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.32,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What happened to helping Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That is still in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:21.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Apparently, I'm good at taking care of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So yet another rival appears against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.18,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.93,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Bye. I've got things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.55,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.73,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,My name's Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.68,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Fujibayashi Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:36.63,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:43.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay, I admit that she was a difficult one to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But you have problems, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:50.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Instead of just reading books,\Nyou should learn how to communicate with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like making jokes and jabbing at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.52,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Jokes and jabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll practice it a little at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your goal is to make a hundred friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.62,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,A hundred friends? Tomoya-kun, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:03.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't have that many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:07.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, you need to jab me back,\Nnot put a question mark on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.06,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Jab…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:16.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck. I can't get along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.47,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like we have a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:22.50,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Be her friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're looking to make her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on, introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.39,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello, Tomoya-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:30.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:34.55,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Um, how are you two related?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Think of us as class ditching buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:40.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Although, I'm a delinquent while she's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.89,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Um, if you don't mind, may I read your fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's perfect for a conversation topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:53.60,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Will she bully me? {ep9}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:56.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.28,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'll read your fortune for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:02.07,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Please pick any three cards you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.97,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,May I see them please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.57,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I don't think you can make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:27.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't deny my efforts like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nothing will change if you run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:34.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You must face reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.29,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Ryou-chan is a bully? {ep9}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.58,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I-I don't think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:40.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You just were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You declared that she won't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.52,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,But there are times when fortune telling fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:54.33,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Even if there's a bad reading, the future should depend on the individual and their surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.80,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Does it work like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:15:01.30,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes. Since I think you're a fun person, too. {ep 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then you'll be her friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:06.17,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes, if that's okay with you. {ep 9 with change}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:12.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How she differs from her vicious sister really helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.53,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Ryou-chan wasn't all that scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:18.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If we weren't talking to Fujibayashi,\Nyou would have weirded the person away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:22.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So first, you have to learn the basics. How to make an introduction:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.75,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.56,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My name is Ichinose Kotomi. A senior in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.11,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My hobby is reading books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:33.51,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you would become my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:36.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Good. We'll practice that during the next break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is there anyone good to practice on…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Tomoyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.01,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,A bear…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're not on patrol, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:49.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maintenance check on the suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Introduce yourself to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.71,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:58.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:01.03,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My name is Ichinose Kotomi. A senior in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.80,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My hobby is reading books.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:06.69,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you would become my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.80,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's so fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you, y'know, like stuffed bears?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:30.71,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.22,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:38.35,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, Okazaki. So that's where you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's eat lunch—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.32,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're the bear that kicked me the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:46.33,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't move from there! I'll get my rezombie on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.33,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Rezombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He always gets a failing grade in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A wonderful kick as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.18,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.32,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,What's this? Ditching class with a girl today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:10.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I am, but she's a true genius, so she's exempt from classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.68,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.37,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My name is Ichinose Kotomi. A senior in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.71,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My hobby is reading books.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:21.80,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you would become my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:27.13,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,I see. So you're the Ichinoses' Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:28.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:31.61,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,I'm sure a lot of those that\Nlive in this city would know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:35.78,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,After all, her parents are amazing scholars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:36.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Scholars?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:41.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are your parents college professors or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.10,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.05,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see. You're made differently from me at the genetic level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.94,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,See, I won't bully you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.53,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Good girl. Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:59.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I thought you don't become friends because you're asked to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.19,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're right. That's why {\i1}I{\i0\fscx50} {\r} approached her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.61,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,But we don't know each other well yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:10.36,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If we go hang out together,\NI'm sure we'll get to know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,With that said, don't you think this is your chance to show how dependable you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:15.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you planning on mooching off of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:19.31,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'll talk to Ryou about it, too,\Nso take us somewhere interesting later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0\fscx40} {\r} is the interesting place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isn't it a nice place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:29.65,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Listen! I was looking forward to karaoke or arcades or fast food restaurants or stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:33.82,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Aren't we being a bother by\Nimposing on this many people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:39.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's rare for this room to become so lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.22,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I created the opportunity for you, so use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.68,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You had better take a step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.85,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.25,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:55.09,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My name is Ichinose Kotomi. A senior in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.68,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My hobby is reading books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:19:00.70,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you would become my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My name is Furukawa Nagisa. A senior in Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My hobby is acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:09.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you would become my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.21,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,My name is Fujibayashi Ryou. A senior in Class D.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.09,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,My hobby is fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:19.06,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you would become my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.64,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,My name is Fujibayashi Kyou. A senior in Class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My hobby is bullying weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:26.60,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you would become my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Whose hobby did you say it was to pick on weaklings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:33.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you see that jab, Kotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's this timing that you have to master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.44,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,U-Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.95,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm actually very strong, so I don't want you to bully me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't get along with you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.43,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,This isn't exactly what I had in mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why don't you all just join the drama club?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:58.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,With this number of people, it would\Nbe enough to convince the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,My apologies to the president, but I'll pass on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:03.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Both Ryou and I don't have any intention of acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:07.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But please come visit often as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:10.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Simply seeing the timing of when\Na jab should happen is a learning experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:18.16,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'll practice a lot, and maybe then\NI'll be able to get a good jab in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're admirable, Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll cheer you on, so good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:26.55,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Please let me join in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:29.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let the three of us work together, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:30.13,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:30.62,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,A really strange group has formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.88,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Let's work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,She looks like she's enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:44.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san's jabs are always very harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I sometimes get—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Kotomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:51.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.45,Note,,0,0,0,,Music Room
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.15,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Um, is there something you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.60,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.75,Default,Gril,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Was it noisy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:11.44,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't bothering us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:14.71,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,A violin…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:22.17,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Would you like to play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.48,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:24.17,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.63,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Kotomi, you can play the violin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:44.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Kotomi! Stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.51,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You're putting too much strength into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:46.53,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You need to relax more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She doesn't hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.25,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:02.67,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya… What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:04.63,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Don't ask me…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:42.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was about to fall into an eternal sleep from the shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:43.78,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:45.40,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:49.78,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Okay. The day after tomorrow, on Monday, we'll hold your violin recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:51.06,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:54.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Isn't Kotomi's violin…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:58.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. She's improved a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:23:59.77,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:01.62,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Therefore…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:05.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,We've been left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:06.44,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.44,0:24:07.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm tired, so I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.75,0:24:08.86,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck?
